    "Once the networks converge, the best model of network G was selected based on the lowest L G value, supplemented by a human-based visual evaluation using the validation image set.",
    "This finalized model of network G, when executed on an Nvidia GeForce RTX 3090 GPU can generate a virtually stained H&E image of 2048 × 2048 pixels within ~0.2 s.",
    "To quantitative evaluate the virtually stained tissue images for the analyses reported in Fig. 6 and Supplementary Fig.",
    "7, we used several metrics, including SSIM, PSNR, number of cell nuclei per FOV, and average size of nuclei, by following the workflow depicted in Supplementary Fig. 4.",
